<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><regulation id="LMS1033938" year.imprint="2025" date.as.at="2025-04-07" date.first.valid="2025-07-01" gazette-only="no" imperial="no" date.gazetted="2025-04-10" date.signed="2025-04-07" sr.no="63" year="2025" series="secondary-legislation" date.terminated="nulldate" sr.type="order"><cover id="LMS1033939"><title>Rates Rebate (Specified Amounts) Order 2025</title><gg>Cindy Kiro, Governor-General</gg><made><heading>Order in Council</heading><made.at>At Wellington this 7th day of April 2025</made.at><made.present>Present:<brk/>Her Excellency the Governor-General in Council</made.present></made></cover><front id="LMS1033940"><pursuant><para><text>This order is made under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM409673" id="LMS1033951">section 3(2)</extref> of the <leg-title href="DLM409295" id="LMS1033952">Rates Rebate Act 1973</leg-title></citation> on the advice and with the consent of the Executive Council.</text></para></pursuant></front><contents><heading>Contents</heading><toc/></contents><body id="LMS1033947" prov-type="clause"><heading>Order</heading><prov id="LMS1033941" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">1</label><heading>Title</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>This order is the Rates Rebate (Specified Amounts) Order 2025.</text></para></subprov></prov.body></prov><prov id="LMS1033942" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">2</label><heading>Commencement</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>This order comes into force on 1 July 2025.</text></para></subprov></prov.body></prov><prov id="LMS1033943" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">3</label><heading>Principal Act</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes"/><para><text><citation jurisdiction="nz"><intref href="LMS1033944" id="LMS1427092">Clause 4</intref></citation> amends the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="DLM409295" id="LMS1033953">Rates Rebate Act 1973</leg-title></citation>.</text></para></subprov></prov.body><notes><amends-note><amends-effective><date>2025-07-01</date></amends-effective><amends-affect><citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="DLM409295" id="LMS1427093">Rates Rebate Act 1973</leg-title></citation></amends-affect></amends-note></notes></prov><prov id="LMS1033944" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">4</label><heading>Section 3 amended (Rates rebate)</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes">1</label><para><text>In <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM409673" id="LMS1033954">section 3(1)﻿(a)﻿(ii)</extref></citation>, replace <amend.in>$31,510</amend.in> with <amend.in>$32,210</amend.in>.</text></para></subprov><subprov><label denominator="yes">2</label><para><text>In <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM409673" id="LMS1033955">section 3(1)﻿(b)</extref></citation>, replace <amend.in>$790</amend.in> with <amend.in>$805</amend.in>.</text></para></subprov></prov.body></prov><prov id="LMS1033945" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">5</label><heading>Revocation</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>The <citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="LMS947627" id="LMS1033956">Rates Rebate (Specified Amounts) Order 2024</leg-title></citation> (SL 2024/43) is revoked.</text></para></subprov></prov.body><notes><amends-note><amends-effective><date>2025-07-01</date></amends-effective><amends-affect><citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="LMS947627" id="LMS1427094">Rates Rebate (Specified Amounts) Order 2024</leg-title></citation></amends-affect></amends-note></notes></prov><prov id="LMS1033946" toc="yes"><label denominator="yes">6</label><heading>Saving</heading><prov.body><subprov><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>A ratepayer’s entitlement to a rebate for a rating year ending before 1 July 2025, and the amount (if any) of that rebate, must be determined as if this order had not been made.</text></para></subprov></prov.body></prov></body><end id="LMS1033949"><signature-block><sig.para align="right">Rachel Hayward,<brk/>Clerk of the Executive Council.</sig.para></signature-block><explnote id="LMS1033948" rule-after="yes" rule-before="yes" series="statutory-regulation" date.as.at="2025-04-07" date.first.valid="2025-07-01" gazette-only="no" imperial="no" date.gazetted="2025-04-10" date.signed="2025-04-07" sr.no="63" year="2025" date.terminated="nulldate" sr.type="order"><heading>Explanatory note</heading><explnote.subhead2>This note is not part of the order but is intended to indicate its general effect.</explnote.subhead2><para><text>This order, which comes into force on 1 July 2025, amends <citation jurisdiction="nz"><extref href="DLM409673" id="LMS1033957">section 3(1)</extref> of the Rates Rebate Act 1973</citation>. That section provides for a rates rebate for low-income home owners.</text></para><para><text>This order—</text><list><item><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>increases the income threshold for a rates rebate from $31,510 to $32,210; and</text></para></item><item><label denominator="yes"/><para><text>increases the maximum rates rebate from $790 to $805.</text></para></item></list></para></explnote><promulgation><issue-authority>Issued under the authority of the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><leg-title href="DLM7298104" id="LMS1033950">Legislation Act 2019</leg-title></citation>.</issue-authority><gazette-date>Date of notification in <emphasis style="italic">Gazette</emphasis>: 10 April 2025.</gazette-date><admin-office>This order is administered by the <ministry>Department of Internal Affairs</ministry>.</admin-office></promulgation></end></regulation>